flavor_text_entries.diamond:
It lives alone, away from others.
Apparently, every one of them
believes it is the most important.
flavor_text_entries.pearl:
Its wings deliver wicked blows that
snap even the thickest of trees.
It searches for prey in icy seas.
flavor_text_entries.platinum:
Because every PRINPLUP considers
itself to be the most important,
they can never form a group.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
It swims gracefully through the frigid sea and sings with a voice
like the roaring tide. It has powerful, sturdy wings and dignity
to match.
